    title: 'Guaranteed Issue Rights for Medicare Supplement Plans',
    summary: 'Guaranteed issue (GI) rights give you the ability to buy a Medicare Supplement (Medigap) plan without going through medical underwriting. They apply in specific situations, most commonly when you lose other coverage. Knowing when your GI rights apply and acting quickly can protect you from being denied or charged higher premiums based on your health.',
