          '**Disenroll from Medicare Advantage.** Once your Medigap approval is confirmed, contact your Medicare Advantage plan or call 1-800-MEDICARE to disenroll. Alternatively, enrolling in a standalone Part D plan will automatically trigger disenrollment from your Medicare Advantage plan.',
